OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny spells Northern Ireland,
OL,6,FEngland and Wales with isolated light
OL,7,Fshowers. Northern Scotland heavy rain
OL,8,Fclearing to sunshine and showers, with
OL,9,Fa chance of afternoon thunderstorms in
OL,10,Fthe northeast. Temperatures above
OL,11,Faverage in the east and southeast but
OL,12,Fcooler overall.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRain and showers across
OL,15,FScotland easing. Cloud spreading in
OL,16,Ffrom the west overnight, bringing rain
OL,17,Ffor some, while most places in the
OL,18,Feast staying clear and dry. Lower
OL,19,Ftemperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
