OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FCloud and rain spreading
OL,6,Feastwards from the west, heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes, especially western areas. Later
OL,8,Fspells and showers follow. Moderate to
OL,9,Ffresh winds, lighter in the north.
OL,10,FTemperatures near normal.
